{"tid":1608313,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"明天千萬唔好搞全港三罷","createTime":"2019-10-01T09:27:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-01T09:37:59.000Z","uid":92339,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"2e89a9de43c8062441371b258e413c5ac41b8118","tid":1608313,"uid":92339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T09:27:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 依家<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">實彈</span></span>都出埋 大家記得要繼續返工呀 <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">千析<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔好</span>罷工呀 </span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一陣返工放工撞到黑警 應該唔會咁好彩命都冇埋啩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔洗驚<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">揾到錢都冇命享</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n返學放學就更加唔好罷課啦 <br />\n你在學年齡返少一兩日學 學校真係會踢你出校架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你係大專生 自資課程 你係客  你俾錢佢賺<br />\n你返少一兩日 佢真係會踢你走唔做你生意架 <br />\n畢業率低影響佢下幾年收客佢都唔介意架<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家聽日千析<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">唔好</span>罷工罷課呀</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /